 808 /// Clones the body of the loop L, putting it between \p InsertTop and \p
 809 /// InsertBot.
 810 /// \param IterNumber The serial number of the iteration currently being
 811 /// peeled off.
 812 /// \param PeelLast Peel off the last iterations from \p L.
